{"tid":774148,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔憤怒 發脾氣【身體語言】+兔兔腳很敏感!","createTime":"2018-08-10T05:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T12:07:22.000Z","uid":197098,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a96841608223e1fedc26710c0596298957d135a8","tid":774148,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子不滿的時候會咕咕叫。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。 <br />\n<br />\n當兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對著你。(這個耳朵擺放與驚慌一樣，但坐姿不同。驚慌的兔子坐姿蹲下) 以下這隻白兔(New Zealand White Rabbit)呈現出憤怒的樣子：(兔子被撫摸或睡覺時，耳朵也是放在後面，所以要看當時情況)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/134224_ddf9c9a45551e218c4018d5c53e9f6bb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F134224_ddf9c9a45551e218c4018d5c53e9f6bb.jpeg&h=fa9e1971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">垂耳兔子憤怒時耳朵會豎起，有時有一點兒向前，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放與垂耳兔驚慌時一樣，但坐姿不同。驚慌的垂耳兔坐姿蹲下) 垂耳兔子舒適時耳朵會放鬆，有時有一點兒向後。<br />\n<br />\n憤怒時如果你撫摸牠，牠可能不理會你而逃去，或撲過來咬你。就算給牠食物，牠亦可能不吃不理會你，直到一段時間後才理會你，要看傷害牠有多深。牠亦可能會不開心不聽話而隨地大便。如果主人在牠面前打開手掌(即是要求牠舔你)，對於兔子來說，這是更加不尊重牠。如果牠屁股對着你(或其他兔子)，就代表牠生悶氣。記住不要打兔子，牠永遠不會忘記的。這會令與主人關係更差，令到害怕了主人而不吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n兔子的腳是很敏感的，所以選擇籠子時，確保底部不是鐵絲綱製造，而是平的，站起來舒服的。否則，牠可能只會站在乾草上，不站在籠子內其他地方，因為鐵絲網令到牠們的腳不舒服。牠們的耳朵和脊椎也是很敏感和易受損的，所以用正確方法抱起兔子，不要抓著耳朵舉起來。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可看到兔兔憤怒而咬人，然後害怕而逃去：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4vCt0losI5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4vCt0losI5s&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=ef543abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4vCt0losI5s</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可看到主人搔垂耳兔兔的腳，兔兔憤怒而咬他:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-7q48ITxeT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-7q48ITxeT8&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=2b1c6834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-7q48ITxeT8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>當兔子用下巴磨擦東西或主人(chinning)時，下巴的腺體能分泌出一種人類聞不到的氣味，以表示這是屬於牠的東西(霸地盤)。</ins>以下video 可看到兔子A 下巴磨擦兔子B的地盤，可以見到兔子B已經憤怒去嚇A，然後屁股對着A(生悶氣):</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCansGFudNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXCansGFudNs&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=6527299c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCansGFudNs</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可在3:00看到垂耳兔憤怒撲過來的時候, 就算主人給牠食物也不吃不理會他：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5mtIM4C-cXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5mtIM4C-cXc&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=9aee1264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5mtIM4C-cXc</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">怎樣令兩隻兔子和睦相處？這個video 有教，步驟簡單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmaH-d1LOxc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHmaH-d1LOxc&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=596b2da1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmaH-d1LOxc</a><br />\n<br />\n更多關於兔子憤怒的身體語言: <a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/why-you-fiend/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Fwhy-you-fiend%2F&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=744afe55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/why-you-fiend/</a> <br />\n<strong><em>領養兔仔：</em></strong><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=57700f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"ecc0a66bb3dca3af5941823368789c5ef0585c75","tid":774148,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:43:24.000Z","msg":"實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=57700f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"4537407eeee8a614cbcd5f38b4bb7a68c0b7260f","tid":774148,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"🐰"},{"pid":"a42e64f021eefc712b6a58b09f747a3e7f0d7c92","tid":774148,"uid":135206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:31:42.000Z","msg":"我嬲 理都冇人理"},{"pid":"374b568e0eec8e4930d081d001b41d0e7e7eae96","tid":774148,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"樓主有玩classic music?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e4774fe27431bece4a91781db181a693636b68","tid":774148,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"374b568e0eec8e4930d081d001b41d0e7e7eae96","tid":774148,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"樓主有玩classic music?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"Prokofiev"},{"pid":"3f4fbea6c602f7dce4b3c9f466d56ad18085563e","tid":774148,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e4774fe27431bece4a91781db181a693636b68","tid":774148,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"374b568e0eec8e4930d081d001b41d0e7e7eae96","tid":774148,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"樓主有玩classic music?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"